Thank you so much for having my work for your first tattoo. 
I was happy to work with you and gave me a lot of meaningful experience.

I‘ve changed my tattoo IG account from @kimsatgat_ttt to @inkkim.kim for some reason. Turns out, it’s wasn’t a good idea to change my IG because my previous clients were having hard time searching my new IG account for a while, including you.

I really appreciate that you found me again and it must took a very long time to find me. 
Sorry for that inconvenience.

Now that we are reconnected. Please reach out to me any time for your new piece.  I will be happy to work with you again.

Thank you Idam for making me feel rewarded and give energy to my professionalism.  .
